{"id":290553,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-厦门市潘涂村村民因土地维权与警察发生/","date":"2013-04-25T11:01:28Z","modified":"2013-04-25T11:01:28Z","title":"维权网 | 厦门市潘涂村村民因土地维权与警察发生冲突（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span>1990</span><span>年，福建省厦门市西柯镇潘涂村的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3500</span><span>亩耕地被出租给凯歌高尔夫俱乐部，为期</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span>年。近期，凯歌高尔夫俱乐部在潘涂村民的土地上盖约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>多套别墅销售，因租地合同期将近，产权无法办理问题，别墅群滞销，于是他们想找潘涂村续签合同。</span></p>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>与潘涂村协商过程中，人们发现了一个秘密，那片土地在合同期满后即将归为国有，而潘涂村民更是无人知晓此事。潘涂村民上告无门，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>，村民自发组织，到高尔夫球场大门前声讨公道，维权持续一个多月，多名村民被抓捕，政府一直没有出面解决，媒体不报道此事。</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨，厦门市当地政府出动近千特警进入潘涂村村民维权现场清场，拆毁村民帐篷、横幅，抓捕、打伤多名村民，有老者被电击枪击晕。上午，数千愤怒的村民开始聚集，并与政府人员、特警发生冲突，多辆警车被砸。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ffSRF8z4_hs/UXjvrYD9puI/AAAAAAAAg08/h5Hc7j43b9o/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ffSRF8z4_hs/UXjvrYD9puI/AAAAAAAAg08/h5Hc7j43b9o/s1600/1.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}